The '''Taurill Overmind''' was the collective hive-consciousness of the [[Taurill/Legends|Taurill]]. It was motivated by a desire to spread the Taurill throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], and to that end reached an agreement with [[Durga Besadii Tai]] in [[12 ABY/Legends|12 ABY]]. The agreement was that the Taurill would aid in the construction of the [[Darksaber (superweapon)|Darksaber]], and in return Durga would help seed them across the galaxy.

